nodes.text: Eiji Kusuhara was a Japanese actor who portrayed a Y-Wing pilot in Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi. Several people, including Lucasfilm's Leland Chee and Kusuhara's longtime friend Hilary Westlake, believe Kusuhara was the actor who played Y-wing pilot Gureni Telsij in the film.
